description: Situated in South Boston's prime West Broadway neighborhood, this exceptionally cared-for 2017 build is not one you will want to miss out on! Some of this home's fabulous features include : White shaker cabinets, quartz countertops, oversized kitchen island, high-end appliances, rich brown hardwood flooring, gas fireplace, modern finishes throughout, and a designer marble bathroom. This home is pouring with natural light, and has a wonderful open layout with plenty of room for living and dining. Tons of closet space throughout as well.  More features include: one heated large garage parking space (included in the list price), central air, in-unit laundry, all in a professionally managed elevator building. This location is a  "Walker's Paradise" just steps to shopping, restaurants, Broadway T Station, and just roughly a half a mile to the lovely South End neighborhood.
